    Having a themes.xml in values-night ensures that the system picks up the dark theme variant.
    The main AppTheme in values/themes.xml already inherits from a DayNight theme, so no specific
    overrides are needed here for the colors to apply correctly.
    -->
    <style name="AppTheme" parent="Theme.Material3Expressive.DynamicColors.DayNight.NoActionBar">
        <!-- You can add specific dark theme overrides here if needed -->
    </style>
</resources>
